snippet.title: Marble Arena 2 Trailer
snippet.description:
http://www.marble-arena.com

Trailer for Marble Arena 2, a fun and exciting, colorful, and absolutely free, marble game. Available December 13, 2011, for Windows, Mac OS, and Linux.
